---
title: Mozzarella and Bacon Paninis with Herby Roasted Potatoes
description: The whole family will love this crowd-pleasing dinner recipe featuring gooey mozzarella paninis. A savoury pesto-tomato sauce adds a grown-up spin to this kid-friendly meal.
